Nurse.

263
00:25:05,213 --> 00:25:07,932
We'll run some tests.
Alert X-ray for a CAT scan.

264
00:25:08,133 --> 00:25:12,365
Call the lab.
We need a complete blood work-up.

265
00:25:24,973 --> 00:25:26,201
John Doe.

266
00:25:27,013 --> 00:25:28,571
Here we are.

267
00:25:34,693 --> 00:25:37,207
Internal Affairs.
Detective Sergeant Goodhart.

268
00:25:37,413 --> 00:25:41,691
My name's Andrea Stewart. I'm calling
from the L.A. Coma Research Center.

269
00:25:41,933 --> 00:25:44,686
I'd like to speak to
Captain O'Malley, please.

270
00:25:45,413 --> 00:25:47,324
What is this in regards to?

271
00:25:47,693 --> 00:25:50,844
I have a John Doe coma patient,
code access 461 -Zebra. . .

272
00:25:51,053 --> 00:25:54,204
. . .with instructions to notify
in case of change in condition.

273
00:25:54,853 --> 00:25:56,081
What's the change?

274
00:25:56,453 --> 00:25:59,763
The patient has come out
of a coma after 7 years.

275
00:26:00,133 --> 00:26:02,203
Nolan, get Hulland, quick.

276
00:26:06,733 --> 00:26:10,646
I'm sorry, Captain O'Malley's
no longer with this division.

277
00:26:11,013 --> 00:26:12,287
I'll take the information.

278
00:26:12,613 --> 00:26:15,605
And please, contact
no one else on this matter.

279
00:26:15,813 --> 00:26:18,202
It would be better
for the patient's welfare.

280
00:26:19,413 --> 00:26:22,723
Ladies and gentlemen,
the President of the United States.

281
00:26:22,973 --> 00:26:26,488
President Bush has caught
the public eye with his antics.

282
00:26:26,733 --> 00:26:29,247
