for Cable Hospital News.

286
00:26:47,013 --> 00:26:48,731
What year is it?

287
00:26:49,733 --> 00:26:52,930
-Try not to talk.
-What year is it?

288
00:26:53,253 --> 00:26:54,811
It's 1 990.

289
00:26:58,293 --> 00:27:00,761
Your charts go back for 7 years.

290
00:27:01,333 --> 00:27:03,847
Do you have any recollection
of anything?

291
00:27:07,173 --> 00:27:09,209
I remember everything.

292
00:27:09,533 --> 00:27:13,685
You're the first patient
to come out of a coma of this duration.

293
00:27:13,933 --> 00:27:16,288
You'll be famous.
You'll be on the news.

294
00:27:16,613 --> 00:27:18,490
Listen to me very carefully.

295
00:27:19,013 --> 00:27:20,412
I'm a cop.

296
00:27:22,053 --> 00:27:24,772
My wife and family were murdered.

297
00:27:25,053 --> 00:27:27,169
That's how I got here.

298
00:27:28,293 --> 00:27:31,490
If you don't get me out
of this hospital. . .

299
00:27:32,253 --> 00:27:35,051
. . .within an hour, we'll both be dead.

300
00:27:35,373 --> 00:27:37,523
You're my cutest patient,
but not my only one.

301
00:27:37,733 --> 00:27:40,167
-You're making a mistake.
-I'll be back.

302
00:27:40,413 --> 00:27:42,483
