303
00:27:49,853 --> 00:27:51,411
How's it going, brother?

304
00:27:52,293 --> 00:27:53,328
Who are you?

305
00:27:53,613 --> 00:27:58,084
I'm Danny, the physical therapist.
I'm going to give you a massage.

306
00:27:58,413 --> 00:28:00,927
-I'll make you feel all right.
-Get the fuck out.

307
00:28:01,133 --> 00:28:03,203
I'll just take you down the hall.

308
00:28:12,013 --> 00:28:15,892
Can I see your list of patients
in your coma care unit?

309
00:28:20,693 --> 00:28:25,130
Get me out. Thanks for the massage,
but stop and get me out of here.

310
00:28:25,453 --> 00:28:28,650
Just relax. You'll get out
of here real soon, I promise.

311
00:28:29,453 --> 00:28:31,523
Morning, Sheri.
How you doing?

312
00:28:36,533 --> 00:28:37,329
Thank you.

313
00:28:38,453 --> 00:28:39,329
Thank you.

314
00:28:45,133 --> 00:28:47,693
-You know that doctor?
-No.

315
00:30:19,693 --> 00:30:21,251
John Doe!

316
00:30:33,413 --> 00:30:34,289
Excuse me.

317
00:30:34,533 --> 00:30:35,761
Doctor?

318
00:30:37,973 --> 00:30:40,771
