322
00:30:57,573 --> 00:30:58,926
Get me out of here.

323
00:30:59,213 --> 00:31:01,249
Don't worry.
I'll take good care of you.

324
00:31:01,453 --> 00:31:03,921
If you want, I'll hook you up
